Sometimes when I open an old ticket in JIRA, I read through the comments section and get a little lost because this ticket has been closed, reopened, tested, resolved, and reopened again, and I can't link the comment to the state it was in at the time of the comment.

So basically, when I'm reading a comment in a ticket, I'd like to know the status of the ticket at the time of the comment -- this helps me understand the relevance of the comment in its workflow.

Thank you.

